        Selling a Property With Solar Panels in Brisbane: What Buyers Want to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Solar panels are common across Brisbane's inner east but they raise specific questions at sale time. Here is what sellers need to understand and disclose before listing.
      </p>
